etro feel.</p>\n<h2>Typography</h2>\n<p>Using <code>Courier New</code>, <code>Monaco</code>, <code>Menlo</code> - classic monospace fonts. The line-height is set to 1.6 for readability, which is important when you're reading code-heavy content.</p>\n<h2>Layout</h2>\n<p>Simple, clean layout. No fancy animations or transitions. Just content-focused. The notes list uses cards with subtle borders that highlight on hover.</p>\n<h2>Code Blocks</h2>\n<p>Syntax highlighting would be nice, but for now keeping it simple with just styled code blocks. The vintage aesthetic doesn't need too much polish.</p>\n</div></main><footer class=\"footer\"><p>Built with Next.js • Deployed on Vercel</p></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-c8441f2d519541e3.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/d753f4838feb0173.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2:I[2846,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[4707,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:I[6423,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[1060,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:[\\\"slug\\\",\\\"2024-01-17-styling-vintage\\\",\\\"d\\\"]\\na:[]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"buildId\\\":\\\"_uB49DAU_UWYsY4PWCQH2\\\",\\\"assetPrefix\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlParts\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"notes\\\",\\\"2024-01-17-styling-vintage\\\"],\\\"initialTree\\\":[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"notes\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"slug\\\",\\\"2024-01-17-styling-vintage\\\",\\\"d\\\"],{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__?{\\\\\\\"slug\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2024-01-17-styling-vintage\\\\\\\"}\\\",{}]}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],\\\"initialSeedData\\\":[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"notes\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"slug\\\",\\\"2024-01-17-styling-vintage\\\",\\\"d\\\"],{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{},[[\\\"$L3\\\",\\\"$L4\\\",null],null],null]},[null,[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L5\\\",null,{\\\"parallelRouterKey